    "shortDescription": "<p>You breathe out a blast of energy. Creatures in the affected area take 1d6 points of energy damage per caster level (maximum of 12d6). A successful Reflex save results in half damage. The spell's effect and energy type depend on the type of dragon scale used: </p><p><i>Black dragon</i>: 60-foot line of acid.</p><p><i>Blue or bronze dragon</i>: 60-foot line of electricity.</p><p><i>Green dragon</i>: 30-foot cone of acid.</p><p><i>Gold or red dragon</i>: 30-foot cone of fire.</p><p><i>Silver or white dragon</i>: 30-foot cone of cold.</p><p><i>Brass dragon</i>: 60-foot line of fire.</p><p><i>Copper dragon</i>: 60-foot line of acid.</p>",
